Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.91,0:00:16.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,[新机动战记-钢弹W]\NJust Wild Beat Communication
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:16.11,0:00:19.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:19.58,0:00:23.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.12,0:00:27.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身 TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.23,0:00:41.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,抱着你被淋湿的肩膀 想温暖你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.44,0:00:49.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,颤抖的指尖 彷徨地在找什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.24,0:00:55.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想留住你的视线
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:56.52,0:01:03.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,相信把悲伤变为力量的爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:06.96,0:01:10.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,受到雨水拍打
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.63,0:01:14.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,决不褪色的炽热思念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:14.27,0:01:17.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,传遍你的全身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:17.97,0:01:19.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,TONIGHT!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:22.54,0:01:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac175年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:25.21,0:01:27.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星的领导者被暗杀了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.02,0:01:30.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,5部钢弹被派往地球
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:30.69,0:01:34.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,本应为了报复
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:34.36,0:01:38.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但OZ在宇宙的行动并非支配
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.93,0:01:41.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,由于他们全面提出和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.66,0:01:44.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,卫星认同OZ了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:46.77,0:01:49.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,Ac195年
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:49.17,0:01:51.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在支配地球和宇宙的进程中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.71,0:01:56.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹被视作叛军\N的象征给孤立了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:56.54,0:02:00.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无家可归的钢弹和其驾驶员
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:00.25,0:02:01.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,在不断转变的时代里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.85,0:02:05.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,以存在意义为赌注继续战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:05.75,0:02:08.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯，快点回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:08.36,0:02:10.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没有你，OZ会容许
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.36,0:02:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,无用的人做出无聊的行动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:23.14,0:02:26.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯，我不能成为你的朋友
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.15,0:02:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,第十九话\N强袭巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.47,0:02:55.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:08.42,0:03:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,大叔，来这边看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.72,0:03:12.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,等一等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:16.09,0:03:18.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,脸色看来很好啊，能起来吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:20.16,0:03:22.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你驾驶着有趣的东西啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:23.13,0:03:25.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我一起捡回来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.17,0:03:28.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想不到除了那些孩子之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:28.14,0:03:31.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,还有驾驶员能驾御那部托尔吉斯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.54,0:03:33.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你是?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.24,0:03:36.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我曾经参加过它的设计
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.54,0:03:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但那是很久以前的事了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.85,0:03:41.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你设计过托尔吉斯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:42.62,0:03:44.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,刚好经过这海域时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.72,0:03:46.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看到激烈的战斗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:46.62,0:03:48.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我真是大开眼界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.96,0:03:51.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,伤口很痛吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.56,0:03:54.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你为何要救我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,你成为OZ的敌人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.00,0:03:58.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,名为杰克斯‧马吉斯的英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:58.87,0:04:00.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,放弃了OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:00.70,0:04:03.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,小心对付你也不用那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.04,0:04:06.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,杰克斯‧马吉斯已经死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.57,0:04:09.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看来是了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.24,0:04:11.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,时代正是迎接转捩点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:11.75,0:04:16.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我想在有生之年看见新的时代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.95,0:04:19.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,果然是部好机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.92,0:04:23.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不愧是钢弹的原型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.76,0:04:27.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那是脱出\N大气层用的喷射器吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我本来打算在钢弹回去宇宙时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.73,0:04:33.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它装在钢弹身上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.97,0:04:37.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,另外，你可以去宇宙吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.71,0:04:38.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,去宇宙?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.91,0:04:41.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙今后会有大变动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:41.64,0:04:44.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,它需要很多优秀的人材
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:47.45,0:04:49.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,开始镇压散布于[洛兰捷点]
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.58,0:04:54.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,旧地球圈统一联合宇宙军的OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.16,0:04:57.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,稳步扩张他在卫星里的势力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:57.83,0:04:59.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,宇宙要塞-巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.69,0:05:03.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是OZ力量的象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.16,0:05:05.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，OZ在卫星居民面前
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.63,0:05:07.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,完全不显露力量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:07.84,0:05:11.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只显露他在宇宙的另一个面孔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.87,0:05:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的蕾蒂‧安上级特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.41,0:05:17.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,代替旧联合作为\N宇宙军的指挥官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:17.21,0:05:19.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和各个卫星的代表团
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.05,0:05:21.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陆续签订友好关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.98,0:05:24.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,随着卫星从联合
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:24.25,0:05:25.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,军事力量的压制中被解放出来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.99,0:05:29.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的新姿态被逐步认同
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.42,0:05:31.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不只卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.19,0:05:34.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,为了地球圈内\N所有人能和平共存
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.30,0:05:38.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在正须要各位的协助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.47,0:05:41.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但很遗憾，卫星里还有人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.64,0:05:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对OZ拘泥于过去错误的历史
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:47.94,0:05:50.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我相信终有一日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.25,0:05:56.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的努力会得到他们的了解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.48,0:05:58.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,那方面我们也有同感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.82,0:06:01.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们会尽力说服各卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.22,0:06:05.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我们无法应付暴力
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.83,0:06:07.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,OZ的存在就是为了那样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,只要有我们OZ
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.56,0:06:12.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,正义一定会有回报吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.03,0:06:13.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,既然蕾蒂‧安特校那样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.00,0:06:15.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我们就放心了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:15.24,0:06:17.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果宇宙得到和平
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.04,0:06:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在仍憎恨OZ的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.17,0:06:21.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,也就一定会觉醒吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.18,0:06:22.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,对
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:22.91,0:06:25.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,蕾蒂‧安特校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.38,0:06:27.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,发现那东西了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.88,0:06:31.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特校，请你回去巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.99,0:06:34.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去巴尔吉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:34.62,0:06:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这是特列斯大人的指示
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.19,0:06:39.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,特列斯大人的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.53,0:06:46.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,回去巴尔吉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.20,0:06:50.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是真的吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.47,0:06:51.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不会有错
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:51.94,0:06:55.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,是载有钢弹从地球升空的HLV
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:55.48,0:06:59.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹是会加害卫星的恶魔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.15,0:07:02.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,很值得利用，成为恶魔的象征
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:02.35,0:07:04.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,派陶拉斯出击!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.42,0:07:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,怎样处置驾驶员?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:06.49,0:07:08.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,看容貌而定
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:08.89,0:07:10.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丑陋的就饶他一命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:10.83,0:07:13.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,会招人同情的就杀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:13.26,0:07:15.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,现在不需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.20,0:07:17.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,妨碍平民意识改革的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:17.73,0:07:21.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,丑陋的就饶他一命…吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.37,0:07:23.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,说笑罢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.18,0:07:30.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,肯定了，是载有钢弹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.01,0:07:32.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,从新加坡升空的HLV
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:32.41,0:07:34.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没能量反应吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:34.62,0:07:37.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,没补给却能飞到这空域
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:37.95,0:07:39.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,光那样已经是奇蹟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.69,0:07:41.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,有可能是无人的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:41.59,0:07:44.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不要紧，命令是收回机体
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.59,0:07:47.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,把它拖回去C102卫星
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:47.26,0:07:48.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.17,0:07:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,什么!?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.85,0:08:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,连新型机也来迎接我真难得呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.48,0:08:09.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但随便接近我的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.15,0:08:10.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,统统要死啊!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.62,0:08:12.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,陶拉斯MD攻击!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.43,0:08:21.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,好快啊!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.04,0:08:32.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,可恶!!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.64,0:08:38.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,这个也没用吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:49.12,0:08:50.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,燃料降到零了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:50.66,0:08:52.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,如果这部死神不能动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.63,0:08:54.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,我也支持不了多久
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:54.83,0:08:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,但是，我不会白死啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:02.84,0:09:06.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,钢弹，你要庆幸是我\N不是MD
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.46,0:09:28.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,虽然我不想模仿希洛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.76,0:09:32.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,和我一起掉落地狱吧!
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.21,0:09:44.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,运气真不好啊，连自爆装置也坏了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.68,0:09:48.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,不对…是好运吧…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.80,0:10:05.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,多次进行破坏活动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:05.53,0:10:07.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,威胁和平的机动战士
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.64,0:10:09.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,!Effect,其中一部钢弹
